 *   The array of order product to render.
 * @param $view_mode
 *    A view mode as used by this entity type, e.g. 'full', 'teaser'...
 * @param $langcode
 *   (optional) A language code to use for rendering. Defaults to the global
 *   content language of the current request.
 * @param $page
